legend bottom left
  |= Layer |= Colour |= Role |
  | Foundation | <color:LightSteelBlue>Blue</color> | Shared utilities: collections, metadata, diagnostics, protection |
  | Domain | <color:DarkSeaGreen>Green</color> | Data model: dictionary, formulas, geo, visibility |
  | Build | <color:NavajoWhite>Orange</color> | Linelist construction: sections, analyses, tables, graphs |
  | Application | <color:Thistle>Purple</color> | User-facing: import/export, setup, designer, dev tools |

